Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:28.74,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信之情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:34.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}擁夜入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:37.85,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影非月  月非影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.23,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫輪回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:49.79,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}盈惑月  消無痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:56.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心結若縛君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:23:07.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}則深信此愛  直至神允  墜天之志
