Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家夥  為什麽會在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麽而生下來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  回答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是親眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座小鎮裏  有著充滿了謎團的殺人集團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在此居住有什麽問題的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹脆就回舊市好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠他絕不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且是先給您一個忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再給我們一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我們都沒有過…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們應該已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年比較特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們想一家人一起克服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然您這麽說  那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄同學  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無變化的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平凡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總覺得發生了什麽事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你驚嚇過度了  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我提前來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  居然丟下她了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴一定生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  難道說和小鈴吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  博士君有些地方還是很遲鈍的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定已經惹小鈴生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  博士君？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  有什麽事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你覺得我是個麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的叔父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個中心的栉名田院長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說我是個奇怪的人什麽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  如果有什麽話要和我說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴請假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天也精神地開始上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時把一誠關在家裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麽說  我們家人必須做點什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十鈴也同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子說不定要不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還有膠囊什麽的  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯  家人一起克服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十鈴  你也要當心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  五十鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果連你也有什麽事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看老哥的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿膠囊來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  你也需要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯防隊那些家夥來過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  之前有說過嫦娥鎮流傳的都市傳說的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個還有些怎麽樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在鎮上的食人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病院的幽靈病房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排成隊伍的紅色螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響徹半夜的野獸叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這些類似的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在鎮上的食人鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是這個城鎮裏住著怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們會襲擊人這樣的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據傳聞怪物半夜在鎮上徘徊尋找食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有人煙的地方襲擊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣襲擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是從人的口中直接吸取生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得像是獵奇電影一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有些事想和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一個傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市傳說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著大鐮刀的少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  昨晚真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個少女襲擊人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是想去報警的  但卻沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上又去了現場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事件的痕迹卻完全不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  拿著大鐮刀的少女的傳聞什麽的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的都市傳說聽過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個沒有聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是這事聽起來挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為博士君來說  算是不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不錯什麽的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有這樣的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是「有其父必有其子」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…這可不是我瞎編的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過還是繼續說給我聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好再說說那個拿著大鐮刀的少女的角色特點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能讓故事更有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  小鈴怎麽回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前都不怎麽請假的  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去時我去看望一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  工作有進展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽說呢  走三步退二步的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒退怎麽行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  最近遇到難關了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  這裏的傳說中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關于拿著大鐮刀的少女的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那是什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話去問同班同學那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同學是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  小要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她擅長的領域吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同學也說不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我更不可能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但姑且會調查一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到哥哥收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  今天不是麻奈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是替過你一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘記了  是是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找1年前遺棄在南極的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對饑餓的兩條猛犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能活下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影  結局——南極物語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近日即將公開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完電影後的用餐可選擇離本院徒步1分鍾的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店  艾特蘭澤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店  艾  特  蘭  澤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔~ 八朔~ 嫦娥的八朔~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸呀~ 酸呀~ 呀呀呀呀呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去丟下垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一誠前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麽！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是一誠前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說會從人的口中吸取生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為會這樣  我們才忠告你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰？  放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你安分點  我們便不會動粗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我們走一趟麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和…  摘花前輩他一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據戒律  摘花一誠先生他應當很快就會受到制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且  你也已經不再是迄今為止的那個你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麽一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是爽斃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽爽的事  為什麽我一直以來都得忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗過了這味道  就再也回不去原先的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回你個頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜天之神  除之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(326,434)\fs24}狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠前輩他…  怎麽了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有些瘋狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣根本就無濟于事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯防隊町田先生叫我傳個話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摘花一誠變成「神人」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石我木雅美  請叔父大人處置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是麽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那邊  明天就由我親自來說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也挺不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴她  今天也休息麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說  哥你被她甩了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不走的話  可要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去叫下她？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她真不太舒服  還在睡的話  可就打擾她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…  太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此  你也別再護著一誠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽你會說出那麽冷淡的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是一家人麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  五十鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想連你也一並失去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:18:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠囊的事應該是機密事項
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是怎麽查出來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這世上  知曉消息的人只要超過了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便不可能保密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打的是什麽算盤？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的又是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一早就說了的麽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想助院長您一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  就像你們醫生為了解患者的病情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要借助病曆卡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的新藥  也得靠著數據來開發
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就沒有聯系過你麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她家  你也沒去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  沒去成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是發生了什麽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也精神地開始上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐回座位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  摘花  正好遲到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可讓我擔心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就先點名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  感冒好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…  昨天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麽事麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠前輩他搬家了…  這…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  小鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六心亂極
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴若闇虛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔之力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔香裏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望鎮邪氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那未曾被我接受的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那難以令我理解的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麽辦…  怎麽做…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來  我還是什麽也辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.61,0:24:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  戀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:29.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:35.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接連著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:48.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口難開 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:54.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}漸次斑駁  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:01:01.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至終焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:07.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之間  逢見君影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:11.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:23.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故鄉迢迢  時之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:26.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:29.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無愛無心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:41.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻蒼空
